--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
IMPROVEMENTS
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

 - Ensure safe defaults if parameter 'nftables_filter_policies' is empty

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
FEATURES
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

 - Add support Podman
 - Add support for table 'mangle', 'nat', 'raw'
 - Add parameter 'nftables_filter_dependencies'
 - Add parameter to configure incoming and outgoing interface
 - Add parameter to configure logging
 - Add dependency to configure sysctl parameters: 'net.ipv4.ip_forward', 'net.ipv6.conf.all.forwarding'

